OL,5,G1900 Police Interceptors
OL,6,     FReality series following
OL,7,     Fhigh-speed police intercept units
OL,8,     Fin West Yorkshire. Duncan pursues
OL,9,     Fa driver treating Wakefield city
OL,10,     Fcentre like his own personal
OL,11,     Fracetrack.
OL,12,G2000 Police Interceptors
OL,13,     FA runaway driver escapes the car
OL,14,     Fwhile still on the move, leaving
OL,15,     FKev to chase him down on foot.
OL,16,G2100 Trauma Room One
OL,17,     FA man arrives in theatre with
OL,18,     Fagonising back pain and doctors
OL,19,     Fsuspect a cancerous tumour is
OL,20,     Fcompressing his spinal cord. He
OL,21,     Fneeds an urgent operation using a
OL,22,     Fhi-tech robot to remove it. (Ep3)
