OL,5,G0155 Skin A&E
OL,6,     FTwo ladies keep Dr Dev Shah busy:
OL,7,     Fone has a large lipoma on her
OL,8,     Fback, the other a cyst on her
OL,9,     Fforehead. 19-year-old Abby hopes
OL,10,     FDr Natalia Spierings can rid her
OL,11,     Fof lumps on her ears.
OL,12,G0245 GPs: Behind Closed Doors
OL,13,     FIn a custom-built mobile surgery,
OL,14,     FGPs have a busy week helping
OL,15,     Fpatients including a boy with an
OL,16,     Finverted chest, a woman with a
OL,17,     Fmysterious rash, and an injury
OL,18,     Fcaused by a horse.
OL,19,G0335 Home and Away
OL,20,     FTane lays down the law. Mackenzie
OL,21,     Fis hurting. Alf and John team up.
OL,22,     FSonny is intrigued by a stranger.
